Project Stories

Connor Delaney Photoshoot



In 2019 I was commissioned to create professional, but artistic headshots for renowned DJ and electronic music producer, Connor Delaney.

 

As per record-label requirement, we required to create images at the highest resolution possible. My artistic vision was to go with a purple color theme for the shoot, as this coincides with Connor’s logo and merch style.



26/06/2019

Hockey League 2020



Last year I was approached by the Wellington-based National Hockey League in order to photograph important matches during the 2020 hockey season.

 

I managed to overcome some of sport photography’s challenges through practice, dedication and buying a special lens in order to capture fast moving imagery accurately. The best photos now hang in their club halls!



15/03/2020

Amy & Graig Wedding



Amy & Graig’s wedding was a very special moment that I had the privilege of capturing through some very personal and intimate photos.

 

The wedding took place in Hawke’s Bay and I was able to capture some of my best wedding photography that day, due to the beautiful sunset that illuminated the field in which the event took place.



02/01/2021
